<% content_for :title, "Your induction programme" %>

<% content_for :before_content, govuk_back_link(
  text: "Back",
  href: schools_cohort_path(@cohort.display_name))
%>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <span class="govuk-caption-l"><%= @cohort.display_name %> cohort</span>
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl govuk-!-margin-top-2">Your induction programme</h1>
    <p>Use an approved training provider</p>
    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Changing your programme</h2>
    <p>Each induction programme is setup differently. Before you change your programme:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>make sure the programme you want to change to works for your school</li>
      <li>if you have confirmed an agreement with a training provider, you need to speak to them</li>   
      <li>check the following advice on what would change on the service</li>
    </ul>
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Using DfE accredited materials</h3>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>your early career teachers and mentors would access the materials and other resources on our service.</li>
      <li>you will need to provide email addresses for your early career teachers and mentors</li>
    </ul>
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Designing and delivering your own programme based on the early career framework (ECF)</h3>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>you no longer need to use this service</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If you need to change your programme, contact: <br><%= render MailToSupportComponent.new %></p>
  </div>
</div>
